name: Space Chaos II
description:
A new Space Chaos scene on every click.
It can take a few seconds before a new scene appears.
Press 'S' to start/end a slideshow (with 8 seconds delay).

This artwork will be randomly generated in your browser. It will always take the full screen, so the effect will be different for different screen ratio's.
Full screen mode (16:9) is recommended.

Written in 997 bytes of pure JavaScript
